```plantuml
@startuml
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

package "class Flyweight(享元模式)" {
    class "FlyweightFactory" as FlyweightFactory {
        C
        - mMap: HashMap
        + getFlyweight()
    }

    class "Flyweight" as Flyweight {
        C
        + dosomething()
    }

    class "ConcreteFlyweight" as ConcreteFlyweight {
        C
        - intrinsicState: String
        + dosomething()
    }
}

note right of FlyweightFactory : 享元工厂
note right of Flyweight : 享元对象抽象基类或者接口
note right of ConcreteFlyweight : 具体的享元对象

FlyweightFactory *-- Flyweight
Flyweight <|-- ConcreteFlyweight

@enduml
```
